  "text": "[36] implemented a white-box evasion attack for PDFRate, a random forest classifier for static analysis of malicious PDF files, by using either a mimicry attack of adding features to the malicious PDF to make it \"feature-wise similar\" to a benign sample, or by creating a SVM representation of the classifier and subverting it using the same method mentioned in [CITATION_1] , assuming the availability of surrogate data for the adversary.",
